Two types of proxies - FORWARD AND BACKWARD 
Forward:The middle layer btwn server and client acts as an proxy in handling the request while hiding the users IP info 
Reverse :hides the info of server snf handles the request

Load Balncer:is typ pf revrese proxy which distributes the traffic among the servers 
  It can distribute the requets using round robin or weighted round robin or Least Connection or Location based or Hashing 
Other types of LB are Layer 4(TCP) and Layer 7(Application)
It is important to have backup load balancer 
